{"tid":1560794,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有啲說話想同頭先六點鬆啲係樂富跳閘嘅妹妹同其他跳閘嘅學生手足講","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:05:24.000Z","uid":2446,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d948580a5fc80e273e5195eae37b980dc717d998","tid":1560794,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔撚好驚，唔好怯</span><br />\n<br />\n你話佢影咗你個樣，之後去搵popo<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，條呀毛的確去咗搵Popo<br />\n<br />\n但係你同我都傾咗兩分鐘有多，<br />\n<br />\n都冇popo出黎捉你！<br />\n<br />\n各位請留意以下幾點保平安：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 跳閘非刑事</span><br />\n唔撚洗驚，除非佢捉住你交比黨鐵職員<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 根本每次跳閘都冇證據影到你跳閘</span><br />\n係呀，你估個撚個都roll住機等捉跳閘咩？<br />\n所有野都係佢講咋<br />\n一係啲藍屍坐定定set cam影閘先有可能<br />\n唔係就只有路過多事藍屍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 如冇人幫要帶佢遊花園</span><br />\n你追到佢出黎，咪就比我見到囉<br />\n如果本身地點冇同路一幫，<br />\n一定要轉場，叫到有同路人幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 適當時運用「被偷怕、被非禮」</span><br />\n如你感到無助，呢啲說話可引起群眾關注<br />\n如未確認同路人，唔好講跳閘住<br />\n呢兩句對中立、淺黃更有效<br />\n有咩事反屈佢犯罪，人多起上黎佢就知驚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">5. 影大頭怕乜撚</span><br />\n由佢影，咪由佢作囉<br />\n反正金魚記憶&amp;fake news,<br />\n佢夠膽放上網，我都話大把人幫你搞返佢轉頭<br />\n而家我就幫你派定心丸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外，其他學生、膽細嘅跳閘者，記住以上幾點，比人捉到走唔甩先好用，最佳做法係<span style=\"color: red;\">跳&amp;run</span>，你要知道好多同路人撐你！</span>"},{"pid":"ab1a22cac3ed3851a8bf59a1089c4ac5e21fe607","tid":1560794,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d56ec86b637d27493a4bf976de2ad24f21513057","tid":1560794,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7501ab77cb0b8faa459fb75ef6514a4534ee49a9","tid":1560794,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242ee5e2beac946c8a7238a9d979162abeb69730","tid":1560794,"uid":36714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"藍咩屍？係屎蟲！記住啦！"},{"pid":"1fdfcaeb1c6be3c5faf1ab9bbc9837a1381399c9","tid":1560794,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c23da2933a990c89c380d62a7e50acf4ad2e9da3","tid":1560794,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPa